ContentDesc_Schloss Kugane: Upon the western coast of Hingashi, caressed by the Ruby Sea, there lies the city of Kugane, the nation's sole open port. Dominating the vibrant cityscape is the majestic Kugane Castle, within whose halls a performance was unfolding, a spectacle to entertain visiting dignitaries. But comedy quickly turned to tragedy when a band of lawless shinobi stormed the castle. Ardently opposed to the influence of foreign nations, these interlopers took all present captive, the lord bugyo of Kugane included. The country now sits on a knife's edge, leaning perilously toward an international incident. Who will see that it falls to the other side?
Instancecontenttextdata_16205_Text: I am the blade of vengeance.They dare only whisper my name─Yojimbo.
Instancecontenttextdata_16206_Text: I want them dead, you hear me? Dead!
Instancecontenttextdata_16207_Text: If you desire my strength, you must pay my price.
Instancecontenttextdata_16208_Text: Come, Daigoro! It is time to collect what is ours.
Instancecontenttextdata_16209_Text: More gold!? B-But I've already... Fine! Just take care of them!
Instancecontenttextdata_16210_Text: Quickly, Daigoro. I would have every coin.
Instancecontenttextdata_16212_Text: They still stand. Impressive...Kageyama! If you would have their heads, I require more gold.
Instancecontenttextdata_16213_Text: You cannot be serious! ...L-Let me check my coffers.
Instancecontenttextdata_16214_Text: Worthy opponents indeed. I will not insult you by holding back any longer.
Instancecontenttextdata_16215_Text: Here. Another payment, as you asked. Now get rid of them!
Instancecontenttextdata_16216_Text: I only do as I am paid to do.
Instancecontenttextdata_16218_Text: Take it! Take it all and bring me their heads!
Instancecontenttextdata_16220_Text: How!? How are they still standing!? This isn't what I paid for!
Instancecontenttextdata_16221_Text: If their price for their lives is beyond your reach, that is not my concern.
Instancecontenttextdata_16222_Text: No, I will not stand for this! I paid for their heads and I shall have them!
Instancecontenttextdata_16223_Text: You will have what your coin is worth, nothing more.
Instancecontenttextdata_16224_Text: No... No! You have to kill them!
Instancecontenttextdata_16225_Text: This is all you would pay me? Very well...
Instancecontenttextdata_16229_Text: Behold, the sword art of legend─Zanmato!
Instancecontenttextdata_16230_Text: Let my blade sing once more!
